#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmousetool; clicks the mouse whenever the mouse cursor pauses briefly. It "
"was designed to help those with repetitive strain injuries, for whom "
"pressing buttons hurts. It can also drag the mouse, although this takes a "
"bit more practice."
msgstr ""
"&kmousetool; klikne miško vsakič, ko se kazalec miške za kratek čas ustavi. "
"Zasnovan je bil za pomoč tistim s ponavljajočimi se poškodbami, ki jim "
"pritiskanje na gumbe boli. Lahko tudi vleče miško, čeprav to zahteva nekaj "
"več vaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmousetool; can eliminate the pain caused by clicking the mouse, and helps "
"many people to use the computer without pain. Unfortunately, some pain can "
"also be caused by simply moving the mouse around the table. If you are "
"experiencing computer-related pain and haven't yet seen a doctor, please do "
"so."
msgstr ""
"&kmousetool; lahko odpravi bolečino, ki jo povzroči klikanje miške, in "
"mnogim ljudem pomaga brez bolečin uporabljati računalnik. Na žalost lahko "
"nekaj bolečine povzroči tudi preprosto premikanje miške po mizi. Če "
"doživljate bolečine, povezane z računalnikom, in še niste obiskali "
"zdravnika, to storite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just to make it absolutely clear: while &kmousetool; can help reduce the "
"pain caused by <emphasis>clicking</emphasis> the mouse, it cannot help any "
"pain caused by <emphasis>moving</emphasis> the mouse. And, like all "
"ergonomic tools, your mileage may vary."
msgstr ""
"Samo da bo popolnoma jasno: medtem ko &kmousetool; lahko pomaga zmanjšati "
"bolečino, ki jo povzroči <emphasis>klikanje</emphasis> miške, ne more "
"pomagati pri bolečini, ki jo povzroči <emphasis>premikanje</emphasis> miške. "
"Kot vsa ergonomska orodja se lahko tudi vaša kilometrina razlikuje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmousetool;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kmousetool;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using &kmousetool; is simple: &kmousetool; watches as you move the mouse, "
"and when you pause briefly, it clicks."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba &kmousetool; je preprosto: &kmousetool; opazuje premikanje miške in "
"ob kratkem premoru klikne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool;'s Smart Drag mode allows you to drag the mouse."
msgstr "Način pametnega vlečenja &kmousetool; vam omogoča vlečenje miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Smart Drag is enabled, &kmousetool; pauses after it clicks down; if you "
"move the mouse, it waits until you stop moving before it clicks up. This "
"way, you can both click and drag the mouse. Smart Drag takes a bit more "
"practice, but becomes natural once you get used to it."
msgstr ""
"Ko je pametno vlečenje omogočeno, &kmousetool; se ustavi po kliku navzdol; "
"če premaknete miško, počaka, da se nehate premikati, preden klikne navzgor. "
"Na ta način lahko kliknete in povlečete miško. Smart Drag zahteva nekaj več "
"vaje, vendar postane naraven, ko se ga navadite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main &kmousetool; window"
msgstr "Glavno orodje &kmousetool; okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool;'s options are accessed mostly via the mouse."
msgstr "Do možnosti &kmousetool; večinoma dostopate z miško."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Start</guibutton>/<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Začni</guibutton>/<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts (or stops) &kmousetool;."
msgstr "Zažene (ali ustavi) &kmousetool;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimum movement:"
msgstr "Minimalno gibanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The minimum movement in pixels before &kmousetool; will attempt to click the "
"mouse."
msgstr ""
"Najmanjši premik v slikovnih pikah pred &kmousetool; bo poskušal klikniti "
"miško."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dwell time (1/10 sec):"
msgstr "Čas zadrževanja (1/10 s):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time the mouse has to pause before &kmousetool; clicks. Try increasing "
"this time if it is hard getting used to &kmousetool;"
msgstr ""
"Čas, ki ga mora miška zaustaviti, preden &kmousetool; klikov. Poskusite "
"povečati ta čas, če se težko navadite na &kmousetool;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart drag"
msgstr "Pametno vlečenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables or disables Smart Drag. Disabled use is easier, so this is the "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči ali onemogoči Smart Drag. Uporaba za invalide je enostavnejša, zato "
"je to privzeto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable <guilabel>Smart drag</guilabel> the <guilabel>Drag time (1/10 "
"sec):</guilabel> field becomes available. This is the time &kmousetool; "
"waits, after it clicks down, before it clicks back up if you don't move the "
"mouse."
msgstr ""
"Če omogočite <guilabel>Pametno vlečenje</guilabel>, postane na voljo polje "
"<guilabel>Čas vlečenja (1/10 s):</guilabel>. To je čas, ko &kmousetool; "
"počaka, potem ko klikne navzdol, preden klikne nazaj gor, če ne premaknete "
"miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable strokes"
msgstr "Omogoči poteze"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmousetool; now supports strokes. When you enable strokes, a slow move to "
"the right and back, followed by a pause, will generate a <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click. A slow move left and back will generate a double click. "
"(Strokes are specified in <filename>$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/config/"
"kmousetool_strokes.txt</filename>. This file is generated by &kmousetool; "
"the first time it is run, but can be modified afterwards.)"
msgstr ""
"&kmousetool; zdaj podpira udarce. Ko omogočite poteze, bo počasen premik v "
"desno in nazaj, ki mu sledi premor, ustvaril <mousebutton>desni</"
"mousebutton> klik. Počasen premik levo in nazaj bo ustvaril dvojni klik. "
"(Poteze so navedene v <filename>$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/config/"
"kmousetool_strokes.txt</filename>. To datoteko generira &kmousetool; ob "
"prvem zagonu, vendar jo je mogoče pozneje spremeniti. )"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Audible click"
msgstr "Slišen klik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plays a sound when &kmousetool; clicks down. This helps, especially with "
"Smart Drag."
msgstr ""
"Predvaja zvok, ko &kmousetool; klikne navzdol. To pomaga, zlasti pri Smart "
"Drag."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with desktop session"
msgstr "Začnite s sejo namizja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, &kmousetool; will start each time the session of the "
"desktop starts."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, &kmousetool; se bo začel vsakič, ko se začne seja "
"namizja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defaults"
msgstr "Privzete nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset all settings to their defaults."
msgstr "Ponastavite vse nastavitve na privzete."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "Ponastaviti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reset all settings to their state when you opened the dialog, or, if you "
"have already saved a setting with the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button, "
"reset all settings to the state when you last pressed <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"Ponastavite vse nastavitve na njihovo stanje, ko ste odprli pogovorno okno "
"ali, če ste že shranili nastavitev z gumbom <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>, "
"ponastavite vse nastavitve na stanje, ko ste nazadnje pritisnili "
"<guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "Uporabiti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "After changing any settings, you must click this button."
msgstr "Ko spremenite kakršne koli nastavitve, morate klikniti ta gumb."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the User manual (this document)."
msgstr "Odpre uporabniški priročnik (ta dokument)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close"
msgstr "Zapri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close the dialog without saving any settings."
msgstr "Zaprite pogovorno okno brez shranjevanja nastavitev."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit"
msgstr "Prenehati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &kmousetool;"
msgstr "Zapri &kmousetool;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "These tips can help shorten &kmousetool;'s learning curve a bit."
msgstr ""
"Ti nasveti lahko pomagajo nekoliko skrajšati učno krivuljo &kmousetool;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the time delays &kmousetool; waits, for both clicking and for "
"dragging."
msgstr ""
"Časovne zakasnitve lahko spremenite &kmousetool; čaka tako na klik kot na "
"vlečenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's best to practice clicking with &kmousetool; using its defaults first. "
"You may especially want to leave Smart Drag disabled at first. Then, once "
"you are comfortable clicking, move on to practicing Smart Drag."
msgstr ""
"Najbolje je vaditi klikanje z &kmousetool; najprej uporabi privzete "
"nastavitve. Morda boste najprej želeli pustiti Smart Drag onemogočeno. "
"Potem, ko vam je klikanje udobno, nadaljujte z vadbo pametnega vlečenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "When using Smart Drag, it may help to enable the Audible Click"
msgstr "Pri uporabi pametnega vlečenja vam lahko pomaga omogočiti zvočni klik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using the Audible Click, you may need to speed up &kde;'s audio "
"response."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabljate slišni klik, boste morda morali pospešiti zvočni odziv &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help! &kmousetool; keeps dropping spurious clicks all over the screen!"
msgstr "Pomoč! &kmousetool; kar naprej spušča lažne klike po celem zaslonu!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are using &kmousetool;, you do have to learn new mousing habits."
msgstr "Ko uporabljate &kmousetool;, se morate naučiti novih navad z miško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, keep in mind where it's safe to click &mdash; clicking on gray parts "
"of windows or non-link areas of web browsers won't hurt anything, so you can "
"safely rest the mouse over those areas until you need it."
msgstr ""
"Najprej ne pozabite, kje je varno klikniti &mdash; klikanje na sive dele "
"oken ali območij brez povezav v spletnih brskalnikih ne bo nič škodilo, zato "
"lahko mirno držite miško nad temi območji, dokler je ne potrebujete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Second, you need to know where you're going to click before you move the "
"mouse. Most of the time, when we know we're going to use the mouse, most of "
"us grab the mouse and start moving it around randomly until we figure out "
"where we want to click. With &kmousetool;, you need to know where you're "
"going to click before you move the mouse in the first place. It is also a "
"good idea to keep your hands off the mouse when you're not using it."
msgstr ""
"Drugič, preden premaknete miško, morate vedeti, kam boste kliknili. Večino "
"časa, ko vemo, da bomo uporabili miško, večina od nas zgrabi miško in jo "
"začne naključno premikati, dokler ne ugotovimo, kam želimo klikniti. Pri "
"&kmousetool; morate vedeti, kam boste kliknili, preden sploh premaknete "
"miško. Prav tako je dobro, da roke ne uporabljate miške, ko je ne "
"uporabljate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "My mouse sticks when I move it. Can I still use &kmousetool;?"
msgstr ""
"Moja miška se drži, ko jo premaknem. Ali lahko še vedno uporabljam "
"&kmousetool;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. If your mouse sticks, it means you need to clean your mouse. This is "
"usually easy to do; the trick is that you have to clean not just the mouse's "
"ball, but the rollers that the ball rolls against inside the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če se vaša miška zatakne, to pomeni, da morate miško očistiti. To je "
"običajno enostavno narediti; Trik je v tem, da morate očistiti ne samo "
"žogico miške, ampak tudi valje, ob katerih se žogica kotali znotraj miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you have to remove the ball. The method for doing this varies from "
"mouse to mouse, but it's usually pretty clear how to do this if you look at "
"the bottom of the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Najprej morate odstraniti žogo. Metoda za to se razlikuje od miške do miške, "
"vendar je običajno precej jasno, kako to storiti, če pogledate spodnji del "
"miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you've removed the ball, you should be able to see the rollers on the "
"sides of the hole that contained the ball. The dirt and grime on them can be "
"easily scraped off with a flat blade or with a fingernail."
msgstr ""
"Ko odstranite žogico, bi morali videti valje na straneh luknje, v kateri je "
"bila žoga. Umazanijo in umazanijo na njih je mogoče zlahka postrgati z "
"ravnim rezilom ali z nohtom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool; clicks down and never clicks up. What's happening?"
msgstr "&kmousetool; klikne navzdol in nikoli ne klikne gor. Kaj se dogaja?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some rare situations, the system suspends &kmousetool; when a drag "
"starts; if you are using Smart Drag, this means that &kmousetool; can never "
"finish the drag by clicking up."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih redkih situacijah sistem prekine &kmousetool; ko se začne vlek; "
"če uporabljate Smart Drag, to pomeni, da &kmousetool; nikoli ne more "
"dokončati vlečenja s klikom navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This happens when you use &kmousetool; under a non &kde; window manager and "
"then use it to move a window."
msgstr ""
"To se zgodi, ko uporabljate &kmousetool; pod ne &kde; upravitelja oken in ga "
"nato uporabite za premikanje okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The solution is to simply click manually; this resets &kmousetool;, and you "
"can then continue to work normally again."
msgstr ""
"Rešitev je preprosto ročno klikanje; to ponastavi &kmousetool; in lahko "
"nadaljujete z normalnim delom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool; moves the cursor when I am trying to type."
msgstr "&kmousetool; premakne kazalec, ko poskušam tipkati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Problem: When you're typing text, &kmousetool; keeps dropping clicks and "
"moving the cursor away from where you want to type."
msgstr ""
"Težava: Ko tipkate besedilo, &kmousetool; nenehno izpušča klike in premika "
"kazalec stran od mesta, kjer želite vnesti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Solution: Use the mouse to place the cursor where you want it, but when "
"you're ready to type, park the mouse on a neutral area on the screen. Then, "
"if you bump the mouse, or if it moves a few pixels, any random clicks that "
"it sends won't matter. Safe places to park the mouse include the gray areas "
"around toolbars and menus, and on the title bars of windows."
msgstr ""
"Rešitev: z miško postavite kazalec, kamor želite, ko pa ste pripravljeni "
"tipkati, postavite miško na nevtralno območje na zaslonu. Če potem udarite z "
"miško ali če se premakne za nekaj slikovnih pik, vsi naključni kliki, ki jih "
"pošlje, ne bodo pomembni. Varna mesta za parkiranje miške vključujejo siva "
"območja okrog orodnih vrstic in menijev ter v naslovnih vrsticah oken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I'm trying to use Smart Drag, but I cannot get the hang of using it to edit "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Poskušam uporabiti Smart Drag, vendar se ne morem navaditi, da bi ga "
"uporabljal za urejanje besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Smart Drag is an advanced feature of &kmousetool;, and takes some getting "
"used to. It is very possible to use it to select text, to cut and paste, and "
"use it in almost any situation where you would normally want to drag the "
"mouse. But you probably won't be able to do this at first. Here are some "
"suggestions:"
msgstr ""
"Smart Drag je napredna funkcija &kmousetool;, na katero se je treba nekaj "
"časa navaditi. Z njim je zelo mogoče izbrati besedilo, izrezati in prilepiti "
"ter ga uporabiti v skoraj vsaki situaciji, kjer bi običajno želeli povleči "
"miško. Toda sprva tega verjetno ne boste mogli storiti. Tukaj je nekaj "
"predlogov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Don't use Smart Drag while you are first learning to use &kmousetool;. "
"Instead, to select text, click at one end of the text, and hold down the "
"shift key while you click at the other end of the text."
msgstr ""
"Ne uporabljajte Smart Drag, dokler se prvič učite uporabljati &kmousetool;. "
"Namesto tega, če želite izbrati besedilo, kliknite na en konec besedila in "
"pridržite tipko shift, medtem ko kliknete na drugi konec besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Audible Click. This will play a <quote>click</quote> sound when "
"&kmousetool; clicks down, and this will tell you when the Smart Drag delay "
"is beginning. With practice, you can use Smart Drag without the Audible "
"Click, but it does take a fair amount of practice."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite zvočni klik. To bo predvajalo zvok <quote>klika</quote>, ko bo "
"&kmousetool; klikne navzdol in to vam bo povedalo, kdaj se začne zakasnitev "
"Smart Drag. Z vajo lahko uporabljate pametno vlečenje brez zvočnega klika, "
"vendar zahteva kar nekaj vaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Know where you're going to click the mouse before you begin moving it."
msgstr "Vedite, kam boste kliknili miško, preden jo začnete premikati."

